name: Single Flared Tunnel (6mm - 16mm)
description:
These single flared tunnels are secure and easy to wear because they are secured by an 'O' ring as opposed to being a screw tunnel. This allows you to wear and remove the plug with incredible ease!

Material: Stainless Surgical Steel
Sizes Available: 8mm (0g), 10mm (00g), 12mm (1/2), 14mm (9/16), 16mm (5/8)

After approximately 6mm, stretchers get too heavy for the ear and cause it to bend up slightly, if left for a long period of time it will heal in a slightly bent position. Tunnels prevent this from happening whilst still allowing your ear to heal and stretch.
